WEBVTT

1.1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.878
Where are your stores?

1.2
00:00:03.878 --> 00:00:07.756
It's one of the first questions — and one of the easiest to get wrong.

2.1
00:00:07.756 --> 00:00:14.490
Never say 'we have stores all across the country' as a vague deflection.

2.2
00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:21.224
If their city isn't on the list, always offer a sample delivery or a video call with an expert.

3.1
00:00:21.224 --> 00:00:25.078
Open today: three Delhi stores — Sultanpur, Kirti Nagar, and Saket at Select City Walk.

3.2
00:00:25.078 --> 00:00:28.933
Mohali.

3.3
00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:32.787
Mumbai at Lower Parel.

3.4
00:00:32.787 --> 00:00:36.641
Surat.

3.5
00:00:36.641 --> 00:00:40.495
And internationally, Gainesville, Florida.

3.6
00:00:40.495 --> 00:00:44.350
Coming up: Bangalore, Indiranagar — about a month out.

3.7
00:00:44.350 --> 00:00:48.204
And Hyderabad, Jubilee Hills — under renovation.

4.1
00:00:48.204 --> 00:00:53.035
Service is pan-India, with international expansion under way.

4.2
00:00:53.035 --> 00:00:57.866
Asked about projects in a specific city?

4.3
00:00:57.866 --> 00:01:02.697
We've done multiple projects across India — I can check with our team about installations in your city.

4.4
00:01:02.697 --> 00:01:07.528
Precise, honest, helpful.

5.1
00:01:07.528 --> 00:01:12.473
Note these.

5.2
00:01:12.473 --> 00:01:17.418
One — never say 'stores all across the country'; be specific.

5.3
00:01:17.418 --> 00:01:22.362
Two — open today: three Delhi stores, Mohali, Mumbai, Surat, and Florida; Bangalore and Hyderabad are on the way.

5.4
00:01:22.362 --> 00:01:27.307
Three — city not listed?

5.5
00:01:27.307 --> 00:01:32.252
Offer a sample delivery or an expert video call.

6.1
00:01:32.252 --> 00:01:35.974
Know the list, keep it current — store status changes fast.

6.2
00:01:35.974 --> 00:01:39.696
Quiz time.

